  "body": "Getting the following message on install of `@truffle/contract` due to a deprecated dependency `highlight.js`.\r\n\r\n`@truffle/contract > @truffle/debug-utils > highlight.js`.\r\n\r\n```\r\n> highlight.js@9.18.5 postinstall\r\n> node deprecated.js\r\n\r\n-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*\r\n\r\n  Verion 9 of Highlight.js has reached EOL.  It will no longer\r\n  be supported or receive security updates in the future.\r\n  Please upgrade to version 10 or encourage your indirect\r\n  dependencies to do so.\r\n\r\n  For more info:\r\n\r\n  https://github.com/highlightjs/highlight.js/issues/2877\r\n  https://github.com/highlightjs/highlight.js/blob/master/VERSION_10_UPGRADE.md\r\n\r\n-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*\r\n```\r\n\r\nNote: It's a large message colored with a red background so it's very annoying. :slightly_smiling_face: ",
