    "body": "I'm still getting this error, even with with the latest version. Here is the output of `npm ls highlight.js` in my project:\r\n```\r\n@sidetree/ethereum@0.1.1-unstable.20 /home/gjgd/sidetree.js/packages/ledger-ethereum\r\n└─┬ @truffle/contract@4.3.1\r\n  └─┬ @truffle/debug-utils@5.0.4\r\n    ├─┬ @trufflesuite/chromafi@2.2.1\r\n    │ └── highlight.js@9.18.5\r\n    └── highlight.js@10.4.1\r\n```\r\n\r\nAs you can see, there are two highlight.js dependencies:\r\n- One that was fixed in https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/pull/3553\r\n- One that still uses the insecure v9.18.5, because @truffle/debug-utils depends on @trufflesuite/chromafi which depends on this insecure version.\r\n\r\nPlease reopen the issue @gnidan ",
